===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|gramarye||lang=enm}}, {{term|gramery||lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|gramaire||lang=fro|classical learning}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|grammatica||lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|γραμματική||lang=grc|tr=grammatike|skilled in writing}}, from {{term|γράμμα||lang=grc|tr=gramma|line of writing}}, from {{term|γράφω||lang=grc|tr=grapho|write}}, from Proto-Indo-European base ''*gerebh-'' (to scratch)

